Class Result<K,​V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.walkertest.core.Result<K,​V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - the type of object to use as the Questions' ids
    V - the type of object to use as the Questions' raw data
    public class Result<K,​V>
extends java.lang.Object
    The Result class represents the result for a test. The scores obtained for each Part are given with the getScoresByPart() method.
